title: Resnet50 + Bounding Boxes [0.628 LB]
description: To wrap up, I take this kernel by @asanakoev and combine it with my idea here about a better classification method to see if it really works. Results:  Better training time (since we only used 68% of data): 5509s vs 8196s.'  A bit better accuracy, the threshold wasn't fine-tuned, it was taken from my original resnet18 kernel, so it can get better.
